headline: Is Analyst Optimism on eBay’s (EBAY) Merchandise Volume Growth Altering the Investment Case?
summary: In recent days, several major analysts increased their expectations for eBay, highlighting anticipated growth in gross merchandise volume linked to strong U.S. consumer spending and favorable exchange rates. This renewed analyst optimism comes as eBay benefits from robust interest in collectibles and expands its capabilities through technology partnerships and new initiatives in key markets. We’ll examine how rising analyst confidence in eBay’s gross merchandise volume growth may influence...
